item.description: We provide FREE pictures with the Easter Bunny at McDonalds. Some kids get the pics before they eat, others afterwards. Depends on the crowd at their time of arrival. This is a great event for us and McDonalds. Set up at 7:30. Make sure signage is up and cameras and printers are ready to go and bunny is in place at 8a. Lots of kids and lots of pictures is the goal!
item.how_to_find_us: It'll be hard to miss. We'll be the ones by the Bunny!
item.name: Breakfast with the Easter Bunny
